Function	Purpose	Examples
Min(argument1, argument2)	Return the lesser of the two arguments.	
Min(2, 4) = 2

Min(9, 4) = 4

Min(Sqrt(2), Sqrt(3)) = 1.4142.....

Max(argument1,argument2)	Return the greater of the two arguments.	
